{
  "stem": "17001.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as we are going, we were taken into a crematorium, because what happened is that during-- what I forget to mention, which is very important.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were taken in to sanitize a few times during our stay.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got different clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how when I arrived, I got the black clothes, black dress.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was selected from my younger sister and the [GERMAN] grab my arm, that was after another how you call them, sterilization or cleaning, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "De-licing, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the name of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So once we were going to be de-liced to-- back to Auschwitz, the town itself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we were going, there was a building, a brick building, far away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a man who was hollering to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is anybody from [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said to him, are you Meier?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, tell-- I said, we are-- we are from Mandok, because my grandparents lived there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I know him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, have you seen my father, or somebody?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Your father and your brother was here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- they should be back soon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, please tell him and my brother, Philip, that we are the three of us here, Clara, Magda, and Elizabeth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And our cousin [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That we are here and coming way back, maybe we could meet them or we could we see them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, you two sisters, [HUNGARIAN] and [HUNGARIAN], I said they are in the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he was happy to hear it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, do you know from anybody else?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And meantime, the [GERMAN] came over and gave me such a bang on my face and my neck that I didn't know how-- how to-- how to survive it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I said, it was worth it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
